  bash ./run.sh help


TASK:
  Create a Terraform setup with an AWS loadbalancer and EC2 app server in a private
  subnet via an autoscaling group. Configure the app server to be reachable through the AWS
  session manager. Create an ansible setup to install, configure and launch Nginx on the
  app server.
  Create a script that creates the app server through Terraform and automatically
  configures the instance through Ansible using Terraform output such as an IP.

  Create a Ruby script to upload and download files to/from S3 using
  the https://rubygems.org/gems/aws-sdk-s3 gem. Make sure that files
  older than 30 days are automatically deleted, but always keep the 10 most up to date files.

